org.spongepowered.api.util.gen

Interface MutableBiomeArea

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BiomeArea

    public interface MutableBiomeArea
extends BiomeArea
    A mutable buffer for BiomeType data. This buffer has no direct relation to the world and changes to it are not synchronized to the world.
